<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="./output.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

    <title>SocketIO login</title>
</head>
<style>
    *{
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }
</style>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-zinc-900 md:bg-gray-200 text-gray-500">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between min-h-screen">
        <div class="w-screen bg-black h-32 rounded-b-3xl p-12 flex justify-center md:justify-normal">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl">Enter chatbox</h2>
        </div>
        <main class="flex-col flex-1 flex items-center md:flex-row md:justify-around">
            <div class="relative mt-16">
                <form method="post">
                <input type="text" class="w-96 h-14 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 p-4 text-white"
                id="username" name="username" placeholder="Username" value="<%= locals.username %>">
                <button type="submit" value="login"
                    class="absolute right-1 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 bg-blue-500 px-2 py-2 rounded-full text-white w-12 h-12 flex justify-center items-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="31.018" height="26.094" viewBox="0 0 21.018 16.094">
                        <path id="sign-in-alt-solid"
                            d="M17.077,79.764H13.629a.494.494,0,0,1-.493-.493V77.629a.494.494,0,0,1,.493-.493h3.448a1.312,1.312,0,0,0,1.314-1.314V67.941a1.312,1.312,0,0,0-1.314-1.314H13.629a.494.494,0,0,1-.493-.493V64.493A.494.494,0,0,1,13.629,64h3.448a3.942,3.942,0,0,1,3.941,3.941v7.882A3.942,3.942,0,0,1,17.077,79.764Zm-1.929-8.251-6.9-6.9a.987.987,0,0,0-1.683.7v3.941H.985A.983.983,0,0,0,0,70.24v3.941a.983.983,0,0,0,.985.985H6.568v3.941a.987.987,0,0,0,1.683.7l6.9-6.9A.994.994,0,0,0,15.148,71.512Z"
                            transform="translate(0 -64)" fill="#fff" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </form>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-24 w-2/5">Here’s some information about this chat.
                Could be anything actually. Like, it’s soo
                cool! Oh my god, it’s amazing! Nothing
                beats this chat. Like, you can talk and
                other people talk back at ya! </p>
        </main>
        <div class="w-screen bg-black h-20 rounded-t-xl"></div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>